Breathe in through your nose and feel your stomach rise. It helps to visualize a balloon filling with air.

[[Stomach2]]
===
title: Stomach2
tags: 
speaker: Rasmus
colorID: 0
position: 843,99
---
Hold your breath without forcing it. Then release your breath and breathe out easily through your mouth. Visualize the balloon releasing its air.

[[Stomach3]]
===
title: Stomach3
tags: 
speaker: Rasmus
colorID: 0
position: 1211,107
---
Repeat breathing in and out, and feel your hands rise and go down on your stomach.

[[Stomach4]]
===
title: Stomach4
tags: 
speaker: Rasmus
colorID: 0
position: 1578,99
---
Try it for approximately five minutes. Try to take more time to breathe out that to breathe in. Redirect your thoughts to your breathing if you are distracted.

